sentences.english: At last node system is debugged.
sentences.chinese: 最后对节点系统进行了连机调试。

sentences.english: If the cutover is successful, the old node is decommissioned.
sentences.chinese: 如果切换成功，旧的节点将退役。

sentences.english: This is a two-node cluster, and you have a third system that will be your administrative console.
sentences.chinese: 这是双节点集群，并且你有另外系统作为管理终端。

sentences.english: If the user is not permitted to see any child nodes, an empty collection is returned.
sentences.chinese: 如果使用者不允许检视任何子节点，则会传回空集合。

sentences.english: The information-driven sensor selection is simulated in this paper.
sentences.chinese: 论文对信息驱动的节点选择机制进行了仿真。

sentences.english: You can extend this pattern to create an entire group of connected nodes.
sentences.chinese: 您可以扩展这一模式，以创建已连节点的整个组。

sentences.english: To obtain the local stress distribution of the K-tubular joint, sub-model was built and calculated.
sentences.chinese: 这是进行其上局部K型管节点疲劳强度分析的前提。

sentences.english: Alternating between a deterministic and a non-deterministic node selection effectively solves the bottleneck problem.
sentences.chinese: 确定与非确定性节点选择交替有效地解决了瓶颈问题。

sentences.english: You should see the two nodes.
sentences.chinese: 您应该看到这两个节点。

sentences.english: MANET is a network where nodes can move arbitrarily in the topology.
sentences.chinese: 在MANET的拓扑中，节点可以任意移动。

sentences.english: This method controls the sending rate for each source node.
sentences.chinese: 这种方法控制每个信源节点的传输速率。

sentences.english: One or more host names can be derived based on the node name of the system.
sentences.chinese: 可以根据系统的节点名导出一个或多个主机名。

sentences.english: And the dangerous offense is a type of criminal attempt.
sentences.chinese: 着手实行是犯罪预备与犯罪未遂的关节点。

sentences.english: Influence of loading path on axial strength of circular tubular TX-joints.
sentences.chinese: 荷载路径对TX型圆管节点轴向承载力的影响。

sentences.english: Eventually, the algorithm reaches a leaf node with the final classification.
sentences.chinese: 最终，算法抵达的叶子节点就是最终分类。

sentences.english: Any number of nodes may be filled-in and any node number sequence may be assigned.
sentences.chinese: 可以创建任意数量的节点和节点次序。
